flowchart LR
    A[Risk Identified] --> B{Meets Risk Appetite?}
    B -- Yes --> C[Accept]
    B -- No --> D{Feasible to Reduce?}
    D -- Yes --> E[Mitigate / Reduce]
    D -- No --> F{Transfer Viable?}
    F -- Yes --> G[Transfer (Insurance / Contract)]
    F -- No --> H[Avoid / De-scope]
    E --> I[Implement Controls]
    I --> J[Residual Risk Reviewed]
    J --> K{Meets Appetite?}
    K -- Yes --> L[Accept]
    K -- No --> H
